Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:10.03,oped,,0,0,0,,前所未見的瞬間 令人激動的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:23.54,oped,,0,0,0,,初出茅廬的我 面對充滿未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:35.30,oped,,0,0,0,,像那一天一色的晨空般 無數次讓我驚訝不已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:45.98,oped,,0,0,0,,現在正鐫刻歷史 胸中也滿溢思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:51.57,oped,,0,0,0,,定能創造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:58.16,oped,,0,0,0,,前所未見的瞬間 令人激動的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:03.79,oped,,0,0,0,,一切都光芒四射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:09.29,oped,,0,0,0,,不為人知的自己 發現未來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:24.56,oped,,0,0,0,,我不懈追尋 那最珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.23,oped,,0,0,0,,永不停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:28.59,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:01.06,oped,,0,0,0,,發生奇蹟的機率
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:06.57,oped,,0,0,0,,根本無法計算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:12.07,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我們相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:19.16,oped,,0,0,0,,或許只是神明的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.30,oped,,0,0,0,,明天的天空會是什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:32.09,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我們去看看 那未知的顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:39.27,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明的心 無法證明之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:44.65,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明之事 那就是我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:50.40,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明的心 無法證明之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:55.99,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明之事 那就是我的心情…或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.54,oped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,262)}那就是我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:08.67,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我才是 承蒙您關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我剛到家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}暈倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}恢復意識了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}現在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:20.37,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,248)}在大學 5點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:20.37,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,422)}打工 5點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:20.37,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,568)\frz359.1}去媽媽的爺爺家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:20.37,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\frz359.1\pos(390,512)}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻暈倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過立刻就讓醫生檢查了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要去接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說是開車送她回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻還笑著說可能是有點睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她又亂來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒什麼 她是去媽媽的爺爺家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他說有和撫子相關的東西想交給小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他的兩座別墅中的一座實在太貴重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我就婉拒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太貴重？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是小櫻現在去的那座別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說是撫子很喜歡那棟房子 就想送給小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}送房子給國中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 所以我婉拒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要喝茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我剛好有點心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:35.69,biaoti,,0,0,0,,小櫻和鏡子和充滿回憶的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你要吃幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給小櫻留幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}四個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我吃兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我把茶泡濃一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}曾祖父長得像媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不好說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我覺得他們眼睛很像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但圓美說撫子和奶奶一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真嬉先生也很想見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有機會再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你害羞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說不定很像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真嬉先生和你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 很像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這下必須讓你們站在一起看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟有血緣關係 自然會很像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我最近也覺得媽媽和小櫻很像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我懂 她們的笑容越來越像了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 也都有種奇妙的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為撫子是個很奇妙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有時會對著空氣說話 還能和不會說話的東西心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這一點你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你不會覺得難以置信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過我什麼都感覺不到 什麼都聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以覺得有點寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻的事也是 我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你知道小櫻的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}詳細的不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 那並不是我能解決的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我只是有所察覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻從四年級開始 就很辛苦的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}爸爸你果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知道有什麼事情卻故意不問 讓我們自由解決
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟是小櫻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不管是自己還是身邊的人 小櫻都很關心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且就算有什麼事 還有你這個可靠的哥哥在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然我是最靠不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這點心好精緻啊 我都不忍心吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我下週開始每週一會在這家店打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}到時候再買點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我很開心 不過你別勉強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再多睡一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}剛才醫生也說沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個 您說有東西要給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能等我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你別太勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉 讓你也擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我沒事的 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是有哪裡痛或者不舒服就一定要說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}無論是多小的事 都別隱瞞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我希望你也能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}打開看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}鑰匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是撫子從小就很寶貝的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是我和妻子從英國帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}英國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}柊澤現在就在英國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫尤那·D·海渡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}D稱號？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是英國的某個魔法師協會授予最高位魔法師的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}尤那·D·海渡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗的傭人可能是魔法師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他們住的那個房子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}曾經被拆掉 改造成了遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}遊樂園？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那為什麼又蓋回了原來的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個地方很適合保存有力量的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也包括那個房子的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那也是魔術師幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你去問過魔法協會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}姑且問了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然幾乎一無所獲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是明白了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}尤那·D·海渡在一年前被逐出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}被逐出那個協會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個協會不是不怎麼管事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只要魔力強大 能完成協會的任務就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他是做了什麼才會被逐出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但我從別的路徑去調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還得到了李家的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小鬼的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知道什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他好像是因為弄丟了魔法協會不外傳的魔法道具才被逐出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}啥 搞丟了？ 他到底是多馬虎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但那只是對外宣稱的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也有傳聞說是他帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}協會會原諒這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不可能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但協會沒辦法讓他還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為沒人能打敗擁有D稱號的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟是那個協會秘藏的魔法道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大概是禁忌之物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}協會懼怕他的力量 也擔心他會使用那個道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以無法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那是多巨大的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他很強大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}比現在的我強是可以肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李家的當家也沒能測出他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}連小鬼的媽媽也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻她 不依靠別人的創造品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}連自己都不曾意識到 就將魔力具現化而創造了卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也就是說 她創造出了自己的魔法道具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然 映出過去的力量是小櫻自己的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你為什麼不告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻的力量很強 但也還很雜亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以說完全不受她控制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 還不知道尤那·D·海渡的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大概和小櫻的新卡牌有關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你不告訴小櫻我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是為什麼不告訴我和月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為你們的表情和態度很容易露陷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為會很擔心小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼 我可是能維持撲克臉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只有你可以 但是月不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這傢伙一涉及到小櫻就會激動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}艾利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能反擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}首先必須掌握對方的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們不用出手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他只是攻擊我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就算這樣也很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也會在這邊盡我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}去幫助小櫻和李小狼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}艾利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 這可是個強敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}艾利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看來是中斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那再聯絡一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不行 呼叫不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這邊也連不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}斯比 斯比呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}露比月也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看來現實的通信手段也被屏蔽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真不愧是柊澤艾利歐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不愧被稱為現存最強的魔法師之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}迄今從未受損過的時鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就算這樣 我也一定要得到新的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為了使用從協會得到的魔法道具 發動那個魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}海渡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然為達目的不擇手段也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是不能丟失最重要的東西啊 尤那·D·海渡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}回去後要馬上休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的 抱歉讓您擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我才是 抱歉這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感謝你們兩個能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以後再來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的 一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我會好好珍藏鑰匙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我 我臉上有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只是覺得我眼中的你 和你眼中的自己是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然我可以直接看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是你想看自己的話 就必須借用鏡子之類的東西對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}最不了解我的就是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說不定讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是有這樣一面鏡子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一面能映出真正的我的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那樣一來 或許我就能知道自己真正的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以及知道怎樣才能不讓大家擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}停在這裡可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再見 你好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 謝謝你 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我家不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個反了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}房子左右反了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一定是卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒關係 沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}無主之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以夢之杖 為吾之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「MIRROR」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「鏡像」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻牌裡也有「MIRROR」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 圖畫也很像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為都是小櫻自己創造的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以出現相似的圖畫也是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 剛剛才在車上說到了鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就出現了相關的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我能試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「飛翔」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以幫我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你就待在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}將卡片的魔力像鏡子一樣映出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「MIRROR」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好難控制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為是鏡子 所以我就想魔法是不是也能被複製出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}結果成功了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}之所以能成功 是因為小櫻的力量足夠強大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}明明你自己並不希望這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}母親和柊澤都說過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「太強的力量會使自己變得不幸」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我絕對 不會讓你變得不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:12.97,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給小可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.02,0:24:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}霧笛在呼喚我 這裡是「交給小可」環節
